# stcmkitpy

STCM (Shipborne Total-field Magnetic) data preprocessor & converter for anomaly detection.

## Features

- Quaternion-based orientation transform
- Calibration using IGRF
- Lowpass filtering & resampling
- `.anm` anomaly output

## Installation

```bash
pip install stcmkitpy
